{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "展梦白在潭底与灰袍老人深谈，老人请求他回金山寺洗清冤名，并在杀死来人后了结自己。展梦白入水躲避时发现潭底奇观与七指仙白风人遗留的铁剑。他持剑杀黑衣蒙面人，却无法下手杀老人，老人遂咬剑自尽。展梦白伪装成小蜻蜓混入洞窟，发现此处正是铸造情人箭的秘密工坊，铜炉铜架间满是绝毒药物。他误入披发少女房间，经审问得知洞内有二三十人，多为下五门绿林与野药郎中。少女欲以警铃要挟，展梦白怒而杀之，警铃大作，敌人施放毒气。他以铁剑破铜门杀出，血战群魔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "在下自后必更谨慎小心，爱惜性命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我尽我所知，俱都告诉了你，不知你也肯为我做两件事么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "在下万死不辞。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你回到金山寺后，必须为我洗清弑杀师兄的冤名，莫要叫我含冤不白而死。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "这件事大师不说，在下也会做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "第二件事，就容易得多了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师但请吩咐。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "等杀了那乘篮而下之人后，便立刻将我杀死。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师！你……你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我秘密已有交待，冤名已可洗清，此身已无所留恋，是以才求你给我个痛快。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师这岂非是强人所难……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你难道忍心看我在这里多受活罪？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "在下只要能活着上去，纵然拼了性命，也要将大师救出此洞，绝不会让大师一人在此受苦。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你且看看我这副样子，纵然离开这里，也是活不下去的了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我此刻除了口中尚能说话，眼中尚能视物，别的已和死人无异，你为何不肯痛痛快快地让我死？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "但大师你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我死在这里，丝毫不觉冤枉，只因自古以来，已有不知多少胜我十倍的英雄豪杰，葬身在此处，你只要看看石上字迹，便可知道了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师可看到七指仙留下的话么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我无事时，便垂首望着这些字迹，想到这些名侠，也遭受到与我同样的悲惨遭遇，心中也不知道是安慰或是难受。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师既看到了，可知道他这句话的含意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "想必有个姓葛的，为了要得到七指仙一件宝物，而将他暗算而死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但那姓葛的却终于未得到那件宝物，想那七指仙死后写了这句话时，心中虽也充满了得意，却又是何等哀痛。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是来了？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你快些入水，听到有铁桶汲水之声，再上来取他性命。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好快的身手，好快的剑锋！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "展公子，你掌中之剑，自何处来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "自潭水中得来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好一柄剑……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师可知道此剑的来历么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "自古以来，不知有多少口名剑，久已绝迹人间，纵是博学之人，也难一一道出来历。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "苍天待你，亦不知是薄是厚，既教你遇着这许多福缘，却偏偏又叫你生在这自古未有的江湖动荡之时，莫非……莫非苍天便是因为这动荡的江湖，而造成你这样一个人物么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你要怎么？为何还不杀了我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "text": "大师受的只是外伤，若能寻得拔毒生肌的灵药，必定能复原的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你在骗鬼么，便是神仙下凡，也无这般灵药能救得了我，你……你还不动手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_pao_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍老人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "再见！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_qing_wa",
      "text": "下面有什么好玩的，你不想上来了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_wa",
      "speaker_name": "青蛙",
      "listener": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "你身子怎地越来越重，咱们越来越瘦，你却越吃越肥，再过一阵，不如把你宰了吃了吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我说小蜻蜓呀，那老和尚这两天怎么样了，难道还挺得住么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "怎么不回话呀，变成哑巴了么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_wa",
      "speaker_name": "青蛙",
      "listener": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "你莫怪他，上次我下去后，也有许久不想说话。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_qing_wa",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_wa",
      "speaker_name": "青蛙",
      "listener": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "那老和尚的样子，实在太惨了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_qing_wa",
      "text": "看不出你心倒蛮好的，只可惜咱们身入此门，便已身不由主，而且……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_qing_wa",
      "text": "你这话只能在我两人面前说说，若是被别人听到，哼哼，你还有命么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "头儿近日脾气越发急躁了，与他初来时仿佛变了个人似的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_wa",
      "speaker_name": "青蛙",
      "listener": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "久困此间，终年不见天日，谁都难免变得如此，你我被逼至此，除了听天由命，还有什么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们在说什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_she_mian_ren",
      "text": "没有什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_she_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "蛇面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少说话，多做事，回房去歇着吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍蒙面人",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "那老和尚还是不肯招么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_meng_mian_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍蒙面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "催梦草不来，如何铸箭，要你这潭水又有何用？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_meng_mian_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍蒙面人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上面只知逼我交箭，却不替我想想如何交法。唉，你们去吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你怎么才回来？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你回来了，还不脱衣裳？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你今天是怎么回事，在外面吓呆了么？好，我来替你脱。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你不是小潘，你……你……你究竟是什么人？怎会来到这里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘切莫声张，否则你就没有命。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "是你没有命，还是我没有命了？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你小子想来偷些野食么？嘿嘿，那你可就看错人了，姑娘我虽非三贞九烈，但却也不能让你随便占了便宜。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "你切莫误会，只要……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "但你也别怕，姑娘我反正也闷得慌，只要你脱了面罩，姑娘若是瞧得中意，也不妨让你……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "放屁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好小子，你偷摸着进来，还敢假正经……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "好人，莫打了，我答应你……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "你！你要怎么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "盖起被来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "我问一句，你答一句，若是有半字虚言，我要你活着比死还难受。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "大……大爷，你不是这里的人么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "这里共有多少人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我也不知道，约摸有二三十人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "他们都是何来历，武功如何？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "他们有的本来是下五门的绿林，专施毒药暗器，有的却是江湖野药郎中，只会些粗浅把式。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "你是什么人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我只是个可怜的良家妇人，被逼而来……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "看你这副模样，也不像是良家妇人，我且问你，他们将你逼来这里，是为了什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "那些人有的是因为无地容身，自愿来此，有的却是被逼而来，这里的头子，为了要他们安心在这里炼箭，便从外面掳了些少女来，让他们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "知道了，这里头子是谁？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "我们都是被逼来的，怎会知道这里头子是谁，大侠客，求求你，饶了我吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "你若真的是良家妇人，他们便不会寻你来了，但你可放心，只要你莫多事，我也不伤你性命。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "对了，姑娘我本就不是良家妇人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "住口，我身后的机簧，直达全窟的警铃，只要我手掌一动，你便没有命了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "对了，乖乖地退回去，只要你听话些，什么事都可商量，说不定……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "披发少女",
      "listener": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "text": "小伙子，告诉我，你是……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "洞外声音",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要动手，施放毒气，让那厮活活在里面闷死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 610
    }
